data.description: Quiet Country living at its best! Single story home on 20 acres with merchantable planted pines. 3 bed/2 bath approx 2200 sq ft heated. 2 car garage with storage. Screened back porch. Hand scrapped acacia hardwood flooring in living, kitchen, and dining rooms. Ceramic tile in laundry and bathrooms. Tile shower in master. Well insulated. All appliances stay except washer and dryer. Will also consider selling house and only 10 acres.
